title: From Out of Nowhere: Part 1
description: The Rangers and Alpha 6 are sucked into an unknown high tech space ship. Meanwhile, Dark Specter assembles many of the universe's most evil villains.

title: From Out of Nowhere: Part 2
description: With the Astro Megaship stranded on an uninhabited planet and Astronema's forces closing in, the Red Ranger reveals his identity to the Rangers and presents them with new powers.

title: Save Our Ship
description: The Rangers return to Earth, and attempt to bond better with alien Andros, who's bemused by our strange culture. Unfortunately, our heroes also get an unfriendly welcome from Astronema who has followed them there (along with her new henchman Elgar), and not only unleashes her cohort Ecliptor on them, but fires upon NASADA, intent on destroying the Shuttle! Meanwhile, Bulk & Skull seek to prove conclusively, without a single doubt, once and for all that aliens exist and are currently targeting Earth (and in the process become rich & famous). To do so, they team-up with a nutty old scientist named Professor Phenomenus. First stop in their quest, NASADA... where they encounter Quantrons!

title: Shell Shocked
description: The Space Rangers meet the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles.

title: Never Stop Searching
description: Carlos stumbles upon Andros watching a video of himself as a child, with his young sister, when she was kidnapped by an unknown creature. Soon, a life-form reading appears on Andros' home world of KO-35, which he assumes is maybe his long lost sister Karone, but what actually awaits him is an ambush by Ecliptor. When this leads to Carlos being injured by following him there, Andros quickly learns the best way to get through his guilt is by relying in others. Meanwhile, Bulk & Skull are led to a watermelon patch by Prof. Phenomenus, who convinces them it's a breeding ground for aliens.

title: Satellite Search
description: NASADA asks the Rangers to help retrieve a crashed satellite with important data on Dark Specter's operations.

title: A Ranger Among Thieves
description: With his four Earthen teammates busy with Math midterms, Andros falls in with a crowd of car thieves at the Surf Spot. Chuck, the ringleader, manipulates Andros' good-natured-ness and turns him, unwittingly, into an accomplice (despite how the other two, Suzi & David, feel guilty about exploiting him). It's only after discovering the three are behind stealing Adelle's delivery van that he learns the truth behind them. But when the Voltage Hog monster attacks the area where the trio are storing the stolen cars, will Andros save his former "friends" despite their wrongdoings? Meanwhile, Prof. Phenomenus convinces Bulk & Skull that a rabbit is actually an alien in disguise.

title: When Push Comes to Shove
description: Cassie loses her diary, which she believes may contain a picture of her that would reveal her identity as a Power Ranger. George, a teen troublemaker, gets ahold of it and uses it as blackmail to make Cassie go on a date with his pal, Lenny, a gentle giant. Meanwhile, Prof. Phenomenus unveils a new plutonium fuel, which plans to use to send Bulk & Skull into space to find aliens. But Astronema becomes aware of this, and has the Elephantitan monster try to topple the skyscraper the fuel is being stored at, in an effort to wipe out Angel Grove. It just so happens to be the same building Cassie & Lenny are having dinner at! Will she Morph in front of him in order to save lives? Or can a new weapon in the Rangers' arsenal arrive in the nick of time?

title: The Craterite Invasion
description: A malfunction with the Megaship's Simudeck releases hundreds of real Craterites into Angel Grove.

title: The Wasp with a Heart
description: Waspicable, a kind-hearted monster from Earth, is torn between his caring nature and his loyalty to his evil brother Sting King.

title: The Delta Discovery
description: The Phantom Ranger discovers where Dark Specter is hiding Zordon.

title: The Great Evilyzer
description: Professor Phenomenus develops a ray that can turn objects evil which Astronema decides to use against the Power Rangers.

title: Grandma Matchmaker
description: Ashley's grandmother visits Angel Grove intent on seeing Ashley engaged before she leaves.

title: The Barillian Sting
description: A suspicious bounty hunter joins forces with Astronema despite Ecliptor's objections.

title: TJ's Identity Crisis
description: Darkonda betrays Ecliptor to increase his own power. Meanwhile T.J. suffers an injury causing him to lose his memory.

title: Flashes of Darkonda
description: Andros makes a startling discovery about his sister's kidnapper and journeys into the heart of Dark Specter's empire searching for answers.

title: The Rangers' Mega Voyage
description: The Power Rangers use their newly-obtained Key Cards to decode the location of a new fleet of Zords.

title: True Blue to the Rescue
description: Justin, the Blue Turbo Ranger, returns to help the Power Rangers.

title: Invasion of the Body Switcher
description: Astronema switches bodies with Ashley to infiltrate the Astro Megaship and capture the Power Rangers.

title: Survival of the Silver
description: The Rangers discover the cryogenically frozen Zhane, the Silver Ranger and Andros' best friend.

title: Red with Envy
description: Andros battles Darkonda and his own jealousy as he worries Ashley might be attracted to Zhane.

title: The Silver Secret
description: After being frozen for two years, Zhane struggles with his weakening Ranger powers.

title: A Date with Danger
description: Zhane struggles between his attraction to Astronema and his duty to help the other Power Rangers.

title: Zhane's Destiny
description: On a desolate planet, the Rangers are captured by a band of resistance fighters prompting Zhane to reconsider his place with the Power Rangers.

title: Always a Chance
description: The Rangers encounter Lizward, who has the ability to change places with another person. During a battle, he changes places with Cassie just as Carlos is about to attack. Carlos ends up injuring his friend. Cassie recovers, but Carlos begins to doubt his abilities as a ranger. He leaves the team for a while and encounters Adam, the person who chose him to be a Ranger. Adam trains Carlos to try and get his confidence back.

title: The Secret of the Locket
description: When Darkonda sets a trap for the Red Ranger, Andros finally comes face to face with his long-lost sister.

title: Astronema Thinks Twice
description: Astronema questions her own motives as she travels to KO-35 to battle the Power Rangers.

title: The Rangers' Leap of Faith
description: The Power Rangers question whether they can trust Astronema when she offers to help them find Zordon.

title: Dark Specter's Revenge: Part 1
description: With a new ally aboard the Megaship, the Rangers race to save the Earth from an asteroid on a collision course with the planet.

title: Dark Specter's Revenge: Part 2
description: An old ally returns to help Andros rescue his sister from Dark Specter

title: Rangers Gone Psycho
description: Astronema assembles a team of evil Psycho Rangers to solidify her power.

title: Carlos on Call
description: A young girl discovers Carlos's secret. And blackmails him to be on call for her which jeopardizes the team.

title: A Rift in the Rangers
description: The Psycho Rangers take advantage of the animosity between the Ranger girls to capture Ashley.

title: Five of a Kind
description: T.J. devises a clever strategy to defeat the Psycho Rangers in battle.

title: Silence Is Golden
description: Able to recognize the Power Rangers' voices, the Psycho Rangers assume human disguises to try and find them when they least suspect it.

title: The Enemy Within
description: While searching for their Mega Voyager, the Power Rangers prepare for a final showdown with the Psycho Rangers.

title: Andros and the Stowaway
description: On a remote planet, Andros befriends a rapidly-growing baby alien on the run from his cruel master.

title: Misson to Secret City
description: Andros and Carlos are trapped inside Astronema's Secret City forcing Andros to discover untapped powers in his Astro Morpher to save the day.

title: Ghosts in the Machine
description: The Rangers race to stop Astronema from using her new device to turn people into Data Cards.

title: The Impenetrable Web
description: Astronema lures the Rangers into a trap on a distant planet.

title: A Line in the Sand
description: A dark Humvee stalks each of the Space Rangers while they're on Earth in their civilian lives. It fails to capture Andros & Ashley while they're out on a date, but succeeds in taking out each of the others. With each it runs down, they're teleported to a barren desert, with no way to contact the Megaship! Even if our heroes can put the brakes on this living vehicle, known as Tankenstein, they'll have even bigger problems with its monster form.

title: Countdown to Destruction: Part 1
description: Dark Specter's combined armies launch a final all-out assault on the entire universe.

title: Countdown to Destruction: Part 2
description: With the forces of evil all but triumphant, the Power Rangers make one last desperate attempt to save Zordon.
